  "reasons": [
    {
      "category": "other",
      "description": [
        {
          "value": "美方不顾中方反复交涉和坚决反对，执意允许台湾地区领导人蔡英文于2023年3月29日\n至31日和4月4日至6日“过境”窜美从事政治活动。美国哈德逊研究所、里根图书馆为蔡\n英文在美从事“台独”分裂活动提供平台和便利，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合\n公报规定，严重损害中方主权和领土完整。",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "The US allowed Taiwan's leader Tsai Ing-wen to \"transit\" through the\nUS for political activities from March 29 to 31 and April 4 to 6,\ndespite repeated Chinese protests and strong opposition. The Hudson\nInstitute and the Reagan Library provided platforms and convenience\nfor Tsai Ing-wen's \"Taiwan independence\" activities in the US,\nseriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US\njoint communiqués, seriously damaging China's sovereignty and\nterritorial integrity.",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "period": {
